Invocation Name: monumental facts
des:
Interested in monuments? Want to know about mysteries surrounding monuments?

Just say, "Alexa open monumental facts" to learn about monuments from around the globe.
Enhance your knowledge, learn, share, stand out in quizzes and more with what you get to know. Curated from around the internet for you.

Enjoy.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
